result.name: Parkview

reviews.text:
The worst pasta I have had ever. The salmon is over cooked, spaghetti have no texture , soft like the baby food. The spicy cod roe is totally fail in this, they are all well done and don’t have spicy flavors. The sauce is super sticky. 
The worst one is that, they use canned mushroom rather than the fresh one. It is dinner and cost about 200hkd. 

The dessert with it is a prepackaged yogurt. Well never pick a restaurant which needless to wait for seat.
decent food with nice services. it is relatively high price to qaulity ratio in New Town Plaza especially the lunch set which includes bread, soup / salad, main course and a drink.
Decent food, but feeling a bit over-priced. That's why a bit disappointed by the quality.

Nice and tasty Afternoon Tea...
The English All Day Breakfast is fine.  Hot coffee good.  And the mango pancakes very nice.
Inexpensive, reasonable quality, but don't have high expectations.

reviews.text:
The worst pasta I have had ever. The salmon is over cooked, spaghetti have no texture , soft like the baby food. The spicy cod roe is totally fail in this, they are all well done and don’t have spicy flavors. The sauce is super sticky. 
The worst one is that, they use canned mushroom rather than the fresh one. It is dinner and cost about 200hkd. 

The dessert with it is a prepackaged yogurt. Well never pick a restaurant which needless to wait for seat.
帶位有禮貌親切，見我推住bb車，特登安排較闊既走廊位，野食唔錯，南瓜薯餅好好食！

貴，食物一般，份量細～新城市廣場所有食店既特色。 
窩夫淋既。
decent food with nice services. it is relatively high price to qaulity ratio in New Town Plaza especially the lunch set which includes bread, soup / salad, main course and a drink.

難食!
生律嘅菜無味!
南瓜唔好味!
漢堡包居然可以無味! 蕃茄無蕃茄! 生菜無生菜味! 連漢堡嘅肉無肉味，好似生乾精咁!
意大利雲吞係叫最正常，但其實都唔見得好食，又咸!
成餐惟一最好味係個包!
最後，明明都無人係門口排隊，仲要催我哋埋單，我哋都未食完!
